  - SNR =  0.0 dB | Wideband VR-ZF: 0.003500 | Wideband VR-MMSE: 0.003152
  - SNR =  5.0 dB | Wideband VR-ZF: 0.000430 | Wideband VR-MMSE: 0.000352
